_:Nc2c19c6e47af4c3eb199f466d3622931 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Tulip Siddiq was Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury and City Minister) at HM Treasury from 9 July 2024 to 14 January 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Hampstead and Highgate in July 2024.</p>\n\n" .
